OL,3,CDrug driver jailed after leading
OL,4,Cpolice on chase in stolen Asda van
OL,6,FA man who stole an Asda van and led
OL,7,Fpolice on a chase through Sussex has
OL,8,Fbeen jailed.
OL,10,FIn January this year, police were
OL,11,Fcalled to Sovereign Harbour Retail
OL,12,FPark in Eastbourne after reports a van
OL,13,Fhad been stolen.
OL,15,FIt had been taken by Shane Brett, 30,
OL,16,Fwho fled the scene and led officers on
OL,17,Fa chase.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
