CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774368667
OL,3,CDrug driver jailed after leading
OL,4,Cpolice on chase in stolen Asda van
OL,6,FThe pursuit came to a halt 16 miles
OL,7,Faway at The Fairway in Newhaven, where
OL,8,Ffootage shows the Asda van trapped
OL,9,Fbetween a police car and another
OL,10,Fvehicle at traffic lights.
OL,12,FBrett was then arrested and a drugs
OL,13,Ftest was carried out. He tested
OL,14,Fpositive for cocaine.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
