PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774368667
OL,3,CDrug driver jailed after leading
OL,4,Cpolice on chase in stolen Asda van
OL,6,FThe next day the 30-year-old was
OL,7,Fcharged with theft of a motor vehicle,
OL,8,Fburglary other than a dwelling,
OL,9,Fdriving a motor vehicle dangerously,
OL,10,Fand driving a motor vehicle on a road
OL,11,For in a public place without third-
OL,12,Fparty insurance.
OL,14,FHe appeared later the same day at
OL,15,FBrighton Magistrates' Court, where he
OL,16,Fpleaded guilty to all charges and was
OL,17,Fremanded into custody.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
